metadata.name: Sadness Overdrive
metadata.description:
"Konbanwa! Purple-Dressed Lady wilted under a cloudy blooming sky. Her lonely footprints demands a glass of wine." 

-

Good evening and welcome to a somber shopping plaza where the girls sing weeping songs and a stray city-ladybird gets drunk on it. we don't need to pick up phone calls. 

-

2022
